    <div class="banner">
        <p>Wondering how to use this?<br />
        <a href="https://github.com/rebelchris/astro-static-tweet#readme" target="_blank">Astro Static Tweet readme</a></p>
    </div>

    <section>
        <h2>Quickstart</h2>

        <Markdown>
            ```bash
            npm i @rebelchris/astro-static-tweet
            ```

            ```jsx
            ---
            import { StaticTweet } from '@rebelchris/astro-static-tweet'
            ---
            <StaticTweet id="1359064894377762816" />
            ```
        </Markdown>
    </section>

    <section>
        <strong>Example 1: <i>Basic text tweet</i></strong>

        <Markdown>
            `<StaticTweet id="1417076547375222785" />`
        </Markdown>

        <StaticTweet id="1417076547375222785" />
    </section>

        
        
        <section>

        <strong>Example 2: <i>Reply to other tweet</i></strong>
